{"tid":2259834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公務員不滿際遇　向飲水機注射母豬激素致五旬同事來經","createTime":"2020-10-27T06:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T06:46:24.000Z","uid":4646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6773099f1f8731c86c521de783b67a55a51a1155","tid":2259834,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:26:07.000Z","msg":"網傳山東威海乳山市統計局在職公務員于某，因對上級人事任命不滿，自2017年8月利用針管注射母豬性激素入辦公室飲水機，令多名同事健康受影響。乳山市公安局近日向內媒證實事件，稱案件已移送檢察機關，正在審理中。<br />\n爆料者聲稱，于某注射母豬性激素後，乳山市統計局上至局長、下至保安，均因飲用這些受污染的水，身體都變得肥胖，「脖子腫得像水桶那麼粗」。女同事更接二連三懷孕，有的一年半載都不來月經，另有幾名已絕經的50多歲大媽竟來月經。<br />\n局長到醫院檢查後，發現體內的丙酸睾丸素、黃體酮、苯甲酸雌二醇嚴重超標，這些激素是給母豬催情刺激交配用的，人不可能接觸到，醫生建議他報警。"},{"pid":"dddebe29e752c7b3511c08eb0e0ade730cebe3f7","tid":2259834,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201026/mobile/bkn-20201026212358252-1026_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20201026%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201026212358252-1026_00952_001.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=72f5e607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201026/mobile/bkn-20201026212358252-1026_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"30c009691cef243b1c770af7cdb9ef62783d3b16","tid":2259834,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:27:47.000Z","msg":"女同事更接二連三懷孕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f459bf5041bb9ea4e518e7b1ab3f53547f504aec","tid":2259834,"uid":61954,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"真.支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa